(Details of any changes will be given in the "Answer changes" section below.)

    [Put an [X] in the box for any configuration with significant answer changes.]

[x] clm6_0 (new)

[x] clm5_1

[x] clm5_0

[x] ctsm5_0-nwp

[x] clm4_5


Bugs fixed
